FASTAPI SETUP :

create virtual environment  - python -m venv  environment_name

To activate -  environment_name/scripts/activate

create file - main.py

install -  pip install fastapi uvicorn

run - uvicon main:app --reload  ||  uvicorn app.main:app --reload (if we create folder inside venv)

Auto Documentation ( postman or thunderclient ) :  http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

DATABASE CONNECTION : (postgresql password : post123)

install - pip install sqlalchemy psycopg2-binary python-dotenv

create .env file with data -  DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:post123@localhost:5432/fastapi_db

create database connection file -   database.py

create model (table creation) connection file -  model.py

create schema file for validating repsonse and request -   schemas.py

